data.description: Assumable VA loan at a 2.25% interest rate! Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this recently updated two-story home seamlessly blends modern comfort with eco-friendly living. The roof is adorned with sleek solar panels, not only enhancing the aesthetic appeal but also reflecting a commitment to sustainability. Upon entering the home, you'll be greeted by the spacious and airy atmosphere created by the high ceilings of the formal living and dining area. The open floor plan offers a gas fireplace that seamlessly connects the family room, breakfast nook, and kitchen. The kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, an island, and a breakfast bar for daily living and entertaining. The home features recently replaced double-pane windows, engineered wood floors, a loft, fresh interior paint, and more! The carefully chosen upgrades and attention to detail make this two-story home a perfect blend of contemporary elegance and comfort, offering a lifestyle of both luxury and sustainability in a peaceful neighborhood. The spacious primary bedroom awaits on the first level and features an updated en-suite bathroom with an expansive walk-in shower with dual rain heads, dual vanities, a toilet room, and a very large walk-in closet. The upstairs consists of three additional bedrooms, a loft, an office area and another renovated bathroom. The attached 3-car garage gives ample parking space with additional pad parking for guests. Outdoors feature an expansive covered patio, a privacy-fenced backyard, and plenty of room to entertain. The solar system ensures reduced electricity cost and dual Tesla batteries can power the house if needed. Come tour this newly listed north central home located in the desirable NEISD conveniently located near restaurants, retail centers, and major highways.
